          To configure the check to check only methods and not variables:
        </p>
        <source>
&lt;module name=&quot;RedundantModifier&quot;&gt;
  &lt;property name=&quot;tokens&quot; value=&quot;METHOD_DEF&quot;/&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
